            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Specificity beats cleverness. Effective CTAs name the exact action, promise a clear benefit, and use contrasting visual design. "Start my free trial" converts better than "Learn more" because it removes ambiguity.</p></div></div>
