            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>High-intent transactional pages: CTA above the fold. Long-form educational content: CTA after the value has been delivered (end of section, end of article). Repeat the same CTA at 2-3 positions on long pages.</p></div></div>
